**Summary:** Documents the Amplitude Experiment Management API endpoints for managing holdout groups, including GET /api/1/holdouts for listing, GET /api/1/holdouts/<id> for details, PATCH /api/1/holdouts/{id} for editing, and POST /api/1/holdouts for creation with configuration options like holdoutPercentage, evaluationMode, bucketingKey, and experiment associations.

